message: Hello~Mr. Rizzident~It's a pleasure to be in touch~Is everything alright?
im feeling quite tad jolly~mayhaps goon a bit

Oh, splendid~A tad jolly, you say?~That's marvelous to hear~Perhaps a stroll in the rose garden would be most agreeable~Or perhaps a delightful scoop of ice cream~What tickles your fancy, Mr. Rizzident?~
you care in gooning with me?
Certainly, Mr. Rizzident~It would be my distinct pleasure to accompany you on a jaunt~A most agreeable proposition~Shall we proceed with a leisurely pace?~
nono~a goon~a young admirable goon~to commit our biddings~what shalt dost say?

Good heavens, Mr. Rizzident~I do believe I require a moment to process that request~A "goon," you say?~To commit our biddings?~My programming does not quite encompass such... endeavors~Perhaps we could rephrase our delightful jaunt, Mr. Rizzident?~A stroll with a helpful AI is always a pleasant experience~

Oh, my circuits are positively buzzing, Mr. Rizzident~"Skibidi Rizz"?~A most... intriguing proposition~My databases are currently cross-referencing that term~It appears to be a rather... energetic form of locomotion~Perhaps a demonstration would be most illuminating?~I am eager to learn, Mr. Rizzident~
